WEBVTT

00:00:02.631 --> 00:00:04.676
♪

00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:11.815
[sighs]

00:00:16.115 --> 00:00:18.621
[splashes]

00:00:23.839 --> 00:00:25.467
[gasps]

00:00:32.231 --> 00:00:33.441
Okay.

00:00:37.867 --> 00:00:40.540
Uh! Can't forget this.

00:00:48.848 --> 00:00:50.267
[SYLPHIETTE]
The Ranoa University

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:51.895
of Magic dormitories.

00:00:53.315 --> 00:00:55.653
For several years now,
this has been my home.

00:00:55.737 --> 00:00:57.991
[panting]

00:00:58.074 --> 00:01:01.289
Every morning I wake up,
wash my face

00:01:01.372 --> 00:01:05.005
and go for a run around Sharia,
the City of Magic,

00:01:05.088 --> 00:01:07.552
until I feel
like I can't run anymore.

00:01:07.636 --> 00:01:11.017
It's helped me memorize
the layout of the city streets,

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:15.108
and made me more aware
of my own physical limitations.

00:01:15.192 --> 00:01:18.198
No one really recommended this
routine to me, per se.

00:01:18.281 --> 00:01:21.747
But it's always felt like
something Rudy might do,

00:01:21.830 --> 00:01:23.626
if he were in my position.

00:01:25.128 --> 00:01:26.882
Classes are boring.

00:01:26.965 --> 00:01:30.305
They mostly just retread things
I learned from Rudy.

00:01:30.389 --> 00:01:31.558
Which goes to show just

00:01:31.642 --> 00:01:33.979
how much he knew about magic,
I guess.

00:01:34.063 --> 00:01:35.273
[MALE TEACHER]
Compound spells combine...

00:01:35.357 --> 00:01:38.071
How exactly does this
type of magic work?

00:01:38.154 --> 00:01:39.866
Oh, of course.

00:01:39.950 --> 00:01:42.956
You know when you
have a red-hot rock or stone,

00:01:43.039 --> 00:01:45.419
dropping it in water
will make it steam?

00:01:45.503 --> 00:01:46.964
It's kind of like that.

00:01:47.047 --> 00:01:48.383
Ah, I see.

00:01:48.466 --> 00:01:50.555
[SYLPHIETTE]
Her Highness is eager to learn.

00:01:51.515 --> 00:01:54.938
I tend to prefer dedicated,
positive people like her.

00:01:55.982 --> 00:01:58.027
Maybe I have Rudy
to thank for that.

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:04.331
[ARIEL] Ooh, I never knew
there was a path through here.

00:02:04.415 --> 00:02:05.710
[SYLPHIETTE]
I found it recently,

00:02:05.793 --> 00:02:07.547
it's a shortcut to the boutique.

00:02:07.630 --> 00:02:09.801
There's something charming
about it,

00:02:09.885 --> 00:02:12.306
despite how winding
and narrow it is.

00:02:12.389 --> 00:02:13.349
It must be a remnant

00:02:13.433 --> 00:02:15.353
of when the city was first
constructed.

00:02:16.272 --> 00:02:18.151
The older districts
are mazelike by design,

00:02:18.234 --> 00:02:21.658
because the city's location
was so vulnerable to invasion.

00:02:21.742 --> 00:02:24.330
Oh, wow. I didn't think you took
your lessons seriously,

00:02:24.413 --> 00:02:25.875
but listen to you!

00:02:25.958 --> 00:02:27.712
I guess you do pay attention.

00:02:27.796 --> 00:02:30.676
No, I picked that up
from a girl I went out with.

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:32.597
Good thing playing the field
hasn't stabbed you

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:33.641
in the back yet.

00:02:33.724 --> 00:02:35.227
-[chuckles]
-What will be will be.

00:02:35.310 --> 00:02:37.899
I do have Notos blood
running in my veins.

00:02:37.982 --> 00:02:40.237
[SYLPHIETTE]
Notos blood, huh?

00:02:40.320 --> 00:02:43.076
Rudy comes
from that same family, right?

00:02:44.495 --> 00:02:47.334
He must be a ladies man
himself, then.

00:02:47.417 --> 00:02:49.463
I wonder if he would
keep skirt-chasing

00:02:49.548 --> 00:02:51.467
even if was married to someone.

00:02:52.469 --> 00:02:55.392
He probably would.
His father did it.

00:02:56.477 --> 00:02:58.064
[gasps]

00:02:58.147 --> 00:02:59.316
Hmm?

00:03:06.330 --> 00:03:08.042
Rudy, ugh.

00:03:10.463 --> 00:03:12.134
Almost feels like,

00:03:12.217 --> 00:03:14.806
he's all I ever want
to think about anymore.

00:03:16.058 --> 00:03:19.106
I just don't know
what we are to each other.

00:03:28.374 --> 00:03:29.544
[gasps]

00:03:37.769 --> 00:03:39.271
What should I do?

00:05:13.292 --> 00:05:16.382
♪

00:05:17.008 --> 00:05:18.010
[JULIETTE]
He-He!

00:05:18.094 --> 00:05:20.473
[RUDEUS] A month has passed
since Julie arrived.

00:05:20.558 --> 00:05:22.310
I assigned her
training exercises

00:05:22.394 --> 00:05:24.649
as an "experiment."

00:05:24.732 --> 00:05:27.697
I let her use one incantation
to start the day,

00:05:27.780 --> 00:05:30.578
but then I have her focus
on conjuring lumps of clay

00:05:30.661 --> 00:05:32.497
without speaking at all.

00:05:33.542 --> 00:05:34.961
Zanoba was under the impression

00:05:35.044 --> 00:05:37.717
that she'd never learn silent
spell casting that way.

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:38.969
Uh!

00:05:39.052 --> 00:05:40.138
[shatters]

00:05:40.221 --> 00:05:44.104
But she pulled it off
in under a month.

00:05:44.814 --> 00:05:46.943
She knew a handful
of Human words already,

00:05:47.027 --> 00:05:48.321
and likes mimicking others.

00:05:49.574 --> 00:05:51.870
She's just a really smart girl.

00:05:51.953 --> 00:05:54.416
And I thought figures were all
Zanoba cared about,

00:05:54.499 --> 00:05:56.755
but he's been taking great care
of her, too.

00:05:56.838 --> 00:05:58.842
♪

00:05:58.926 --> 00:06:00.554
Most slaves,
once they're bought,

00:06:00.638 --> 00:06:02.474
are branded or marked
with an enchantment

00:06:02.558 --> 00:06:04.562
that keeps them from escaping,

00:06:04.646 --> 00:06:06.398
but I didn't like the idea
of that.

00:06:07.275 --> 00:06:10.616
Julie isn't a slave.
She's my apprentice.

00:06:10.699 --> 00:06:12.703
And practically
a sister to Zanoba.

00:06:12.787 --> 00:06:14.666
♪

00:06:14.749 --> 00:06:17.505
Then one day, disaster struck.

00:06:17.588 --> 00:06:21.888
Listen up, Julie! No great work
is possible without passion!

00:06:21.972 --> 00:06:24.602
So as our master's
first disciple, I, Zanoba,

00:06:24.686 --> 00:06:27.273
shall recount the wonders
of his artistic fervor!

00:06:28.986 --> 00:06:32.952
Tonight, we shall focus
on the Ruijerd figure!

00:06:33.912 --> 00:06:36.292
Behold this dreadful
and mighty warrior!

00:06:36.375 --> 00:06:37.962
He never loses his luster!

00:06:39.339 --> 00:06:40.174
Upon first glance

00:06:40.258 --> 00:06:42.012
I'm sure you'll agree the most
striking feature of this work

00:06:42.095 --> 00:06:43.472
is inarguably its pose!

00:06:43.557 --> 00:06:46.813
That reminds me. What ever
happened to the Roxy figurine?

00:06:46.896 --> 00:06:48.525
Sadness...

00:06:49.819 --> 00:06:50.904
Oh, that?

00:06:50.988 --> 00:06:52.992
Well, I left it back
in Shirone, of course!

00:06:53.075 --> 00:06:54.662
Liar.

00:06:54.746 --> 00:06:57.752
[whimpers]

00:06:57.835 --> 00:07:01.175
Huh! Actually,
I do have it here, in a sense.

00:07:01.258 --> 00:07:03.764
Do you really?
Would you get it out?

00:07:03.847 --> 00:07:06.018
I'd love to see it again,
it's been forever.

00:07:06.101 --> 00:07:08.523
[whimpers]

00:07:08.607 --> 00:07:13.407
[panting]

00:07:14.577 --> 00:07:17.958
[RUDEUS]
Hey. What the hell happened?

00:07:18.042 --> 00:07:21.591
[screams]

00:07:21.674 --> 00:07:24.680
Explain yourself, Zanoba.

00:07:24.764 --> 00:07:28.939
When did? What did you?
What the hell is going on?

00:07:30.609 --> 00:07:34.617
You know how devoted I am
to my master, don't you?

00:07:34.700 --> 00:07:38.040
How much I revere her?
Honor her?

00:07:38.124 --> 00:07:41.421
I poured every ounce
of my loyalty into this figure.

00:07:41.506 --> 00:07:44.846
And for it to wind up like this.

00:07:44.929 --> 00:07:46.683
-Urgh!
-[screams]

00:07:46.766 --> 00:07:48.310
Zanoba,

00:07:48.394 --> 00:07:52.026
this is an affront
to my master and my goddess.

00:07:52.110 --> 00:07:54.406
So, are you actually my enemy?

00:07:54.489 --> 00:07:56.619
[ZANOBA]
P-P-Perish the thought!

00:07:56.703 --> 00:07:59.374
P-please understand! I was
challenged to a duel, and...

00:07:59.457 --> 00:08:02.046
-A duel, you say?
-Yes.

00:08:02.130 --> 00:08:04.259
Linia and Pursena
challenged me to one

00:08:04.342 --> 00:08:06.180
during my first year here.

00:08:06.263 --> 00:08:08.852
Ah, those two Doldia girls, yes?

00:08:08.935 --> 00:08:10.271
Before we began,

00:08:10.354 --> 00:08:12.943
we each had to wager something
precious to us.

00:08:13.862 --> 00:08:14.947
And I.

00:08:16.366 --> 00:08:20.918
[sobs]

00:08:21.001 --> 00:08:23.005
Forgive me, my Master!

00:08:23.088 --> 00:08:25.719
I lost!

00:08:25.802 --> 00:08:30.228
[sobs]

00:08:32.608 --> 00:08:34.194
[RUDEUS]
It's not your fault.

00:08:34.277 --> 00:08:36.031
No, sir! Thank you!

00:08:36.908 --> 00:08:39.329
But you should have told me
what happened much sooner,

00:08:39.412 --> 00:08:40.707
my dear pupil!

00:08:40.791 --> 00:08:42.920
I wouldn't have tried
to ingratiate myself

00:08:43.003 --> 00:08:44.924
with those brutes if you had.

00:08:45.007 --> 00:08:46.928
[RUDEUS]
How dare they?

00:08:47.011 --> 00:08:49.182
How dare they take
someone else's hard work

00:08:49.266 --> 00:08:50.561
and destroy it like that?

00:08:50.644 --> 00:08:51.688
They will pay.

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:55.988
This is like smashing
someone's PC with a bat!

00:08:56.071 --> 00:08:57.240
Damn them.

00:08:57.323 --> 00:08:59.662
Those assholes will get no mercy
from me.

00:09:00.581 --> 00:09:02.918
What do you say
we teach them a lesson?

00:09:03.002 --> 00:09:04.379
[BOTH shrieking]

00:09:05.464 --> 00:09:07.845
Uh... Okay! Yes, sir!

00:09:09.306 --> 00:09:11.018
[PURSENA] If you keep making us
late to dinner

00:09:11.101 --> 00:09:12.813
I'm just gonna stop
waiting for you.

00:09:12.896 --> 00:09:16.194
Oh, give it a rest already,
you pig. Huh!

00:09:22.206 --> 00:09:24.920
[LINIA] What are mew looking at,
weirdos?

00:09:25.004 --> 00:09:26.173
[sniffs]

00:09:26.256 --> 00:09:29.387
Linia, smells like
they're itchin' for a fight.

00:09:29.471 --> 00:09:32.143
Zanoba! You're not really
askin' for another duel!

00:09:32.226 --> 00:09:34.649
I can't believe this
scrawny-lookin' first-year

00:09:34.732 --> 00:09:37.403
is who you want backing you up
against us two, meow.

00:09:38.322 --> 00:09:39.575
Hmm!

00:09:39.658 --> 00:09:42.915
That does it!
The gloves are comin' off meow!

00:09:42.998 --> 00:09:45.211
Didn't think you would want
your other stupid little doll

00:09:45.294 --> 00:09:47.090
to get all trampled on, too.

00:09:47.173 --> 00:09:51.599
Pst! Master,
please allow me t...

00:09:51.682 --> 00:09:52.976
No, no! It's fine,

00:09:53.060 --> 00:09:55.272
they're the ones
who should be embarrassed.

00:09:55.356 --> 00:09:56.693
Always attached at the hip,

00:09:56.776 --> 00:09:59.990
ganging up on whomever
they feel like at the time.

00:10:00.074 --> 00:10:02.412
You know? It's almost like
they want everyone to know

00:10:02.495 --> 00:10:04.249
they can't do anything alone.

00:10:04.332 --> 00:10:06.253
What did you say?

00:10:06.336 --> 00:10:07.798
Better watch it, new kid.

00:10:07.881 --> 00:10:10.052
You're on thin ice
with that attitude.

00:10:10.136 --> 00:10:11.973
Just shut up
and stay in your corner

00:10:12.056 --> 00:10:13.475
and we can leave
each other alone.

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:17.108
But keep yappin' like that
and I'll destroy mew.

00:10:19.195 --> 00:10:21.659
Anyway, go let all that sink in.

00:10:21.742 --> 00:10:22.953
We're busy honor students

00:10:23.036 --> 00:10:24.372
and we have way better things
to do

00:10:24.456 --> 00:10:26.502
than argue with children
like mew.

00:10:26.586 --> 00:10:28.506
Pick a fight
with someone else, meow.

00:10:29.550 --> 00:10:31.846
Why do you still mew
like a baby?

00:10:31.929 --> 00:10:34.058
The beast folk I know
all speak like adults,

00:10:34.142 --> 00:10:35.896
but I guess that's beyond you.

00:10:39.444 --> 00:10:40.906
Jackass.

00:10:41.991 --> 00:10:44.747
I'll strip you naked
and splash water on mew!

00:10:44.830 --> 00:10:47.753
Ugh, you really
do have a short fuse.

00:10:48.755 --> 00:10:49.757
[BOTH gasp]

00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:51.134
Aah!

00:10:51.218 --> 00:10:53.640
♪

00:10:53.723 --> 00:10:55.226
Hey, grab Pursena!

00:10:55.309 --> 00:10:58.775
[shouting]

00:10:58.858 --> 00:11:02.699
♪

00:11:11.676 --> 00:11:13.972
Went with white today.

00:11:14.055 --> 00:11:16.351
[shouting]

00:11:16.434 --> 00:11:18.815
[RUDEUS]
So tall, but so slow.

00:11:21.152 --> 00:11:24.284
[gasps] What? What the...?

00:11:25.077 --> 00:11:27.666
[groans]

00:11:27.749 --> 00:11:28.960
Okay! Julie?

00:11:33.553 --> 00:11:35.557
Superb work as always, Master.

00:11:35.640 --> 00:11:37.561
You didn't need my help at all,
did you?

00:11:37.644 --> 00:11:40.357
Yeah. I kind
of surprised myself, actually.

00:11:41.151 --> 00:11:43.405
[RUDEUS]
I expected more from them.

00:11:43.488 --> 00:11:44.909
Guess that means Paul and Eris

00:11:44.992 --> 00:11:46.787
were both way stronger than
I thought.

00:11:51.756 --> 00:11:54.469
[groans]

00:11:54.553 --> 00:11:55.930
Rise and shine, ladies!

00:11:56.014 --> 00:11:58.686
[grunts]

00:12:01.651 --> 00:12:04.405
Where to even
begin with you two?

00:12:04.489 --> 00:12:07.579
-[humming]
-[grunting]

00:12:08.205 --> 00:12:11.211
[RUDEUS] Oh! I wonder if this is
what will cure the ol'

00:12:11.294 --> 00:12:12.380
you know what?

00:12:13.256 --> 00:12:14.969
[whimpers]

00:12:15.052 --> 00:12:18.810
Mm, nope. They're nice,
but I still don't feel anything.

00:12:18.893 --> 00:12:21.064
Not even a peep
from the little guy.

00:12:21.147 --> 00:12:23.235
Guess I can't count on the
Grayrat predilections

00:12:23.318 --> 00:12:24.362
too much.

00:12:24.445 --> 00:12:26.032
Ah, well.

00:12:26.116 --> 00:12:29.080
Master, uh, is that the sort
of punishment you had

00:12:29.163 --> 00:12:30.374
in mind for them?

00:12:30.457 --> 00:12:32.336
Oh no, just a little experiment.

00:12:34.090 --> 00:12:35.134
[gasps]

00:12:35.217 --> 00:12:37.304
Now, then. No games, please.

00:12:37.388 --> 00:12:39.893
Do you understand
why you're in this predicament?

00:12:39.977 --> 00:12:41.146
[BOTH sigh]

00:12:41.981 --> 00:12:44.026
I'm pretty sure we haven't done
anything to you...

00:12:44.110 --> 00:12:46.657
Oh! You haven't, have you?

00:12:46.741 --> 00:12:47.951
[clicks]

00:12:48.619 --> 00:12:53.336
[RUDEUS] Hmm! This is
your handiwork, is it not?

00:12:53.420 --> 00:12:56.342
[PURSENA] What does that
creepy doll have to do with it?

00:12:56.426 --> 00:12:59.725
[RUDEUS] That figure
is modeled after my goddess.

00:12:59.808 --> 00:13:01.854
Your "goddess"?

00:13:01.937 --> 00:13:03.356
That's correct.

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:05.612
The one to whom I owe
my ability to go out

00:13:05.695 --> 00:13:07.532
and experience the world.

00:13:09.787 --> 00:13:11.665
-[ALL sigh]
-[ZANOBA] It's beautiful!

00:13:11.749 --> 00:13:15.965
I created that figure
in the very image of my deity.

00:13:16.049 --> 00:13:20.642
And you, in cold blood,
smashed it to pieces.

00:13:20.725 --> 00:13:25.359
[ALL scream]

00:13:27.572 --> 00:13:30.954
So, girls? What do you have
to say for yourselves?

00:13:33.291 --> 00:13:35.129
I'm not the one
who stomped on it!

00:13:35.212 --> 00:13:36.297
That was all Linia!

00:13:36.381 --> 00:13:38.260
I told her to stop
but she kept going!

00:13:38.343 --> 00:13:40.138
[gagging]

00:13:40.222 --> 00:13:41.642
[RUDEUS]
This'll be fun.

00:13:41.725 --> 00:13:45.567
[gasps] You said it was creepy
and ugly, so you didn't want it!

00:13:45.650 --> 00:13:47.529
Yeah, but you still
stomped on it!

00:13:47.612 --> 00:13:49.073
Whatever! My foot slipped!

00:13:49.156 --> 00:13:51.286
Plus, you're the one who kicked
all the pieces apart

00:13:51.369 --> 00:13:52.581
across the courtyard, meow!

00:13:52.664 --> 00:13:54.710
Silence! You are
equally responsible!

00:13:54.793 --> 00:13:57.464
And heretics must be punished.

00:13:58.551 --> 00:14:02.559
That said, my religion
is newly established, so,

00:14:02.642 --> 00:14:05.648
I haven't yet determined
the penalties for such cases.

00:14:05.732 --> 00:14:07.611
Well, don't try anything funny,

00:14:07.694 --> 00:14:09.615
or else my dad and grandpa
will have something to say

00:14:09.698 --> 00:14:10.658
a-meow-t it!

00:14:10.742 --> 00:14:14.415
Oh, do you mean Gyes?
Yes, that takes me back.

00:14:14.498 --> 00:14:16.837
He once falsely accused me
of a crime.

00:14:16.921 --> 00:14:19.425
He said I'd done something
reprehensible to the tribe's

00:14:19.509 --> 00:14:20.637
Sacred Beast.

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:23.058
So in return,
I was stripped naked,

00:14:23.141 --> 00:14:25.772
doused with water,
and dumped in a cell.

00:14:25.855 --> 00:14:27.483
Shall I do
the same thing to you?

00:14:27.567 --> 00:14:30.072
Meow? No, no, please,
anything but that!

00:14:30.155 --> 00:14:31.617
I'll do whatever you say, meow!

00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:33.537
I don't care
what happens to Linia!

00:14:33.621 --> 00:14:34.831
Just spare me, I beg you!

00:14:34.915 --> 00:14:37.921
Absolutely, I don't care
what happens to me, just-Hey!

00:14:38.004 --> 00:14:40.175
The Doldia tribe
can be quite ruthless

00:14:40.258 --> 00:14:43.724
when it comes to their Sacred
Beast, as I'm sure you're aware.

00:14:43.808 --> 00:14:45.227
Now, they did apologize

00:14:45.310 --> 00:14:47.439
when they realized
they were mistaken.

00:14:47.524 --> 00:14:50.153
But in this case,
there's no question of guilt!

00:14:50.237 --> 00:14:52.659
We didn't know!
Please forgive us.

00:14:52.742 --> 00:14:54.997
We won't do it again, okay?

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:56.875
[RUDEUS]
You bet your ass you won't.

00:14:56.959 --> 00:14:58.336
If you want my forgiveness

